OL,3,CPolice 'reassurance patrols' after
OL,4,C'threatening message' sent to schools
OL,6,FA DUP MLA has said schools in the
OL,7,FAntrim area have been threatened and
OL,8,Fpolice are investigating.
OL,10,FPolice said an email was sent to
OL,11,Fmultiple schools and businesses and
OL,12,F"reassurance patrols" have been
OL,13,Fincreased in the area. It has been
OL,14,Freported bomb warnings have been sent
OL,15,Fto schools in a sinister email.
OL,17,FUTV understands around 10 schools are
OL,18,Faffected and none have had to close.
OL,20,FSouth Antrim DUP MLA Trevor Clarke
OL,21,Fcondemned the online message.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/6
