OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1779397867
OL,3,CPolice 'reassurance patrols' after
OL,4,C'threatening message' sent to schools
OL,6,FHe said: "This email appears to have
OL,7,Fbeen sent to people associated with a
OL,8,Fnumber of schools and specifically
OL,9,Freferences Antrim. Whilst any threat
OL,10,Fmust be taken seriously, it is
OL,11,Fimportant that alarm is not caused
OL,12,Funnecessarily and the wording of the
OL,13,Fmessage does raise some questions.
OL,26,@nD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
