PN,44703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1779397867
OL,3,CPolice 'reassurance patrols' after
OL,4,C'threatening message' sent to schools
OL,6,F"The message has also been shared
OL,7,Fonline and is there is an
OL,8,Funderstandable concern on the part of
OL,9,Fparents in particular. I want to
OL,10,Freassure them and the wider community
OL,11,Fthat I have community that I have
OL,12,Fspoken to police this morning, and
OL,13,Fthey have opened an investigation. It
OL,14,Fis important that we follow any advice
OL,15,Fwhich the police give to school
OL,16,Fleaders.
OL,18,F"Whatever the background to this
OL,19,Fmessage it is important that whoever
OL,20,Fsent it is identified and dealt with
OL,21,Fappropriately."
