PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1779397867
OL,3,CPolice 'reassurance patrols' after
OL,4,C'threatening message' sent to schools
OL,6,FIn a statement, the PSNI said: "Police
OL,7,Freceived reports today, Tuesday 19th
OL,8,FMay, of an email having been sent to
OL,9,Fmultiple schools and businesses in the
OL,10,FCounty Antrim area.
OL,12,F"Officers are investigating the
OL,13,Fcontents included within this email,
OL,14,Fand are conducting a number of
OL,15,Fenquiries.
OL,17,F"Reassurance patrols have also been
OL,18,Fincreased in the areas affected, in
OL,19,Forder help keep our communities safe.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/6
