PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1779397867
OL,3,CPolice 'reassurance patrols' after
OL,4,C'threatening message' sent to schools
OL,6,F"We would urge anyone to report
OL,7,Fanything suspicious to police on our
OL,8,F101 number, always 999 in an emergency.
OL,10,F"Police will also be engaging with
OL,11,Fanyone affected including schools,
OL,12,Fbusinesses and our partner agencies
OL,13,Fthroughout the course of today as our
OL,14,Fenquiries continue."
